      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A meeting of all the subcommit-\ntees for the trades council carnival is\ncalled for tonight at headquarters,\nover the Warwick, at s o'clock. All\nmembers are desired to be present.\nas consideration of several new\nschemes is to be had.\n\n\nManager Burch has a design for a\nbutton which is expected to be a\nfeature, of the campaign.\n\n\n1t is announced that the Brother\nhoods Of Locomotive Firemen and\nEngineers and the trainmen will\nprobably join with the trades coun-\nell in promoting the carnival."
    }
  ]
